text: Hombach may refer to: *Bodo Hombach (born 1952), German politician, member of the SPD *Hombach (Ochtum), a river of Lower Saxony, Germany, tributary of the Ochtum *Hombach (Westerbach), a river of Bavaria, Germany, tributary of the Westerbach *Schmelzbach, other name Hombach, a river of North Rhine- Westphalia, Germany, tributary of the Sieg
title: Hombach
